{{>layout/header}}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="p-5 mb-4 bg-light rounded-3">
        <div class="container-fluid py-5">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold">4910 Collection</h1>
            <p class="col-md-8 fs-4">트렌디한 4910 아이템을 실시간으로 만나보세요.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="mb-3">🔥 4910 추천 상품</h3>

    <div class="row">
        {{#items}}
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                    <a href="/item/{{id}}">
                        <img src="{{imgUrl}}" class="card-img-top" alt="{{name}}" height="300" style="object-fit: cover;">
                    </a>

                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="text-secondary mb-1" style="font-size: 0.9em;">{{brand}}</p>
                        <h5 class="card-title text-truncate">{{name}}</h5>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mt-3">
                            <span class="fw-bold">{{price}}원</span>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-dark">구매하기</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/items}}

        {{^items}}
            <div class="col-12 text-center py-5">
                <p>현재 등록된 상품이 없습니다. 서버를 재시작하면 크롤링이 시작됩니다!</p>
            </div>
        {{/items}}
    </div>
</div>

{{>layout/footer}}